<body>
    <h1>T1 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"8868e2e1bfbe" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">1. Introduction</h1>
<p local-id=3D"cf037a9eea2d"><strong>1.1 Purpose</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"0b47fde51476">This document describes the implementation of =
a containerized Node.js application deployed on AWS using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a456239b-799e-4edb-b5eb-781c9d847466">
<li local-id=3D"71fb4a44-ed60-4712-a605-d6a961c195f5">
<p local-id=3D"ae363e2a1dc3">Docker</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3d6fed3-08db-4348-8eb3-8081908dc6f8">
<p local-id=3D"db52bfdda94a">Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81231fdf-c0d0-4dc8-b4fb-dba8e2768766">
<p local-id=3D"be7e986d4cc4">Amazon ECS (Fargate)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ddaf3c8e-7713-4f9a-8a15-a0c7c4429a4d">
<p local-id=3D"1c8462d7fe1c">Application Load Balancer (ALB)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"accd11f1431a">The intended audience includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3b0d1f16-1ee3-4826-809f-9d7b4e32c7e6">
<li local-id=3D"3e119c96-4cdd-49c4-b30c-3a39785b244b">
<p local-id=3D"08c0511eb641">Mentor / Reviewer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"886653a7-53f5-4fe6-8f07-af21d1834000">
<p local-id=3D"f15cd99f13ff">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7f033fc7-0374-41ab-b512-76a6014aff69">
<p local-id=3D"18f05b10ec62">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"458041569912">The goal is to clearly explain what was implem=
ented and how it works.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"40030287-6e49-47d5-8a6f-054353cb5150">
<p local-id=3D"4d23b3d4bed0"><strong>1.2 Scope</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c405f5060cad">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9470c584-32cf-4f55-b04b-7c60881271ef">
<li local-id=3D"82b9c91c-c2e8-4b28-a3b8-13630757fb24">
<p local-id=3D"a292b2d40b63">Containerization of the Node.js application</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"2679fe20-9d1c-4578-ae4a-fbb0fd8d434b">
<p local-id=3D"8c457cf31200">Image storage in Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1510d168-0bc3-4523-a581-dffaf7e61e15">
<p local-id=3D"7dbb9ce16542">Deployment using ECS Fargate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d16713c-39ff-4643-8a6a-d6d0cb15426d">
<p local-id=3D"9de8b244ea81">Load balancing using ALB</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a838b858-a804-4a74-8f33-342cd7b3d35a">
<p local-id=3D"a958629db800">Networking and security configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0ea37d6e144c">This implementation was performed manually via=
 AWS Console and CLI.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"24578c2b-b926-4150-9a25-2a28c2ecee92">
<h1 local-id=3D"7bd9bbd33cbf" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<p local-id=3D"05b5d61a7fb4"><strong>2.1 Definition</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"894f146413fa">This project demonstrates a basic container-ba=
sed deployment workflow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6fc301a8-5d60-4471-bd74-da5c4d0feea6">
<li local-id=3D"ef4e1428-5e4d-4686-8a9d-4be9e6d6e72c">
<p local-id=3D"e81b977dc9f3">Build Docker image</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"97eb6796-2ef4-4acf-9ea6-79dadf6f6dde">
<p local-id=3D"3f2d1ee512b9">Push image to Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"305e1234-e75c-4991-80fa-8c61aecf5748">
<p local-id=3D"ad27afa1df2b">Deploy container using ECS Fargate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db8b888a-17a0-4065-9e04-70005cf8c777">
<p local-id=3D"2f0a6e773bf3">Expose application using Application Load Bala=
ncer</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"8fa635bf7ca7">It replaces manual EC2-based application hosti=
ng with a managed container approach.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"32402686-28b5-44bb-abfa-b2e3f8eaeab1">
<p local-id=3D"4af5a5d62522"><strong>2.2 Key AWS Well-Architected Principle=
s Applied</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a6282b5104b9">Only what was actually implemented:</p>
<p local-id=3D"56bd96b15e7a"><strong>Operational Excellence</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a41ca537-74db-403a-a0ea-502193db5bb3">
<li local-id=3D"1aa21195-7cb9-499c-9854-966844422dfd">
<p local-id=3D"13f74304df57">Used managed AWS services (ECS, ALB, ECR)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"b7e03482-ed0b-4cae-ad28-5a194034067c">
<p local-id=3D"a27bbeca1f5d">Deployment tracked via ECS service health</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6fdcb90b7107"><strong>Security</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"93cd19fb-59a9-4b05-bfb9-36653bab140a">
<li local-id=3D"08668f8c-e9ac-4dd1-a476-9866ee78e5a5">
<p local-id=3D"9731b04c718f">Private ECR repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74413cef-6948-4c92-ac56-1322d4697c0a">
<p local-id=3D"ea5268194818">Security groups restricting access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"303842b3-de71-4364-af99-caf7f1cdb3b8">
<p local-id=3D"5470d8e5183d">Containers not directly exposed to the interne=
t</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d6cbeea-a572-42fb-a7f2-b5582d31338d">
<p local-id=3D"fc3baf28a18e">Only ALB is internet-facing</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5121387d5824"><strong>Reliability</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3275674f-eb15-41fa-8ce0-8c161cc7864a">
<li local-id=3D"98aa8359-774f-435c-9291-a698be7ec064">
<p local-id=3D"29a891c65d6a">Desired task count set to 2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"425dd86c-576d-4133-9c5f-4cda022525f3">
<p local-id=3D"befd2fc49bf8">ECS automatically restarts failed tasks</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"e944cb31-f159-4f9e-919f-67d92da2ca5d">
<p local-id=3D"9e546af7e04e">ALB health checks remove unhealthy targets</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"35e4effaebba"><strong>Performance Efficiency</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"afdb54b8-1e93-494b-ac6c-78e644393f50">
<li local-id=3D"bb5bbc41-6eb2-4655-b361-76736a319302">
<p local-id=3D"8ab72564ae93">Lightweight container (256 CPU / 512 MB)</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e6549e83-0b7c-4f8a-addf-14bd76d6de77">
<p local-id=3D"e57434bc35f0">Load balancing across two tasks</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"105887daa669"><strong>Cost Optimization</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"cf4d370e-be9d-4241-ac4c-f1b1924e493d">
<li local-id=3D"3f3b41f5-505f-48ad-bead-3e1a9c24ca1a">
<p local-id=3D"f703bd287c12">Used Fargate (no EC2 instances)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04265983-b941-49b9-af1b-1bdbc71d2c16">
<p local-id=3D"b391fdbab9c2">Right-sized container resources</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"31d4f1888c5b"><strong>Sustainability</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0a9f8070-0de5-48cc-bceb-e2d7f5486dbc">
<li local-id=3D"21626b14-4e13-4783-9982-29d1e8008d5f">
<p local-id=3D"652ff0926933">No idle virtual machines</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aafd234c-c688-486b-940c-51fa6bbd3ee4">
<p local-id=3D"4a0df7a13b56">Serverless compute usage</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e5bfcc0b-d3e0-4baf-ade1-169ea101d2ec">
<p local-id=3D"e5b8180dbd17"><strong>2.3 Goals and Objectives</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ed266ca-bd35-41ee-8300-e5f620033473">
<li local-id=3D"f6dd96b2-7342-464b-aec6-6beff76a3167">
<p local-id=3D"28331ee7f6ef">Containerize a Node.js application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c7553d95-3ee0-4a94-b2d4-fc81ce09be12">
<p local-id=3D"09efa5bc6383">Deploy without managing EC2 servers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e0e34053-3226-4e29-9fc7-cfa62d0a812e">
<p local-id=3D"0675e6c61e64">Ensure high availability using 2 running tasks=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc5da485-21b1-4555-ae58-9f2bdeab3682">
<p local-id=3D"933d7272f0c8">Securely expose application to the internet</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1e7f20ee-3995-47de-89fd-03a89a685e00">
<p local-id=3D"14c20319bf16"><strong>2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</stron=
g></p>
<p local-id=3D"2097da056737">Constraints:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"575fa304-5c94-4e99-bf42-55ed13cd7b48">
<li local-id=3D"026e30cb-47ae-4203-bf1d-5b435b5cce54">
<p local-id=3D"6d7945562e17">Single region (us-east-1)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cc1a144-4ad9-4a59-99c0-7c4734a343fc">
<p local-id=3D"1a870f2598c7">Minimal resource sizing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b72dc94-89d1-4f68-b1a0-ff0cc18beed5">
<p local-id=3D"aa75f224f1f0">Manual setup (no automation)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9ffca63288c9">Assumptions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3bbdea60-b4ec-46e2-b509-590f70489d0b">
<li local-id=3D"ffa12baa-015e-46be-9c99-427f730ed396">
<p local-id=3D"743b20b58f93">Stateless web application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88904b95-f0ca-4e75-b96a-ff7132732a93">
<p local-id=3D"609428f3ea20">Public HTTP access required</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"dfa2b7e6-566e-48ec-bc6c-38d66fa49b32">
<h1 local-id=3D"2281c0914102" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c712e3819a7d"></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-5-2026-12_16=
_24-AM-20260304-184816.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"045de01d1=
0dbd165f7c3a4897118a8107b0a4ac859b8a299b76e9832984edfb9" data-image-src=3D"=
https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1785266204/diagram-e=
xport-3-5-2026-12_16_24-AM-20260304-184816.png?version=3D1&amp;modification=
Date=3D1772650123996&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"643"=
 data-width=3D"1674" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resour=
ce-id=3D"1830420495" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resourc=
e-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"diagram-export-=
3-5-2026-12_16_24-AM-20260304-184816.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.a=
tlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-lin=
ked-resource-container-id=3D"1785266204" data-linked-resource-container-ver=
sion=3D"5" data-media-id=3D"43b655a1-0e1f-4358-8b2c-9999ce47fbe9" data-medi=
a-type=3D"file" height=3D"179"></span>
<p local-id=3D"98f163611437"></p>
<p local-id=3D"d141926d8fae"><strong>3.1 Infrastructure Overview</strong></=
p>
<p local-id=3D"ee19a046eebb">The following screenshot confirms that the Doc=
ker image was successfully pushed to the private Amazon ECR repository.</p>=
<span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper conflu=
ence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-ce=
nter" alt=3D"image-20260218-144724.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=
=3D"0a6492cb718d9f0ea5b19fa9a7d1df851391d9dd2fd63df48e22873003191393" data-=
image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1785266=
204/image-20260218-144724.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1771426048=
076&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"231" data-width=3D"46=
8" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"178565940=
5" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachme=
nt" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260218-144724.png" data-b=
ase-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-=
type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1785266204" data-li=
nked-resource-container-version=3D"5" data-media-id=3D"47766ed3-f4d5-4058-b=
2f6-df2c0d1d39ac" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"230"></span>
<p local-id=3D"f4a53ebe5816">Components Used:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ee18b070-731f-46c3-ba81-ecbc279064a1">
<li local-id=3D"7529caeb-415e-4629-952b-c98b7ae110de">
<p local-id=3D"26ee447954ee">Docker (local build)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c1cea328-b3cf-443a-87d8-4c430983a49c">
<p local-id=3D"bd52fce04dab">Amazon ECR (private image storage)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f79844a1-50a9-49df-9f5c-7ffc25767f54">
<p local-id=3D"719aaad31811">Amazon ECS Cluster (Fargate)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d40d3835-057b-41cc-b5cc-1971ea18ccb4">
<p local-id=3D"6c7f90ae267e">ECS Task Definition</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f130e0b8-7893-42db-8507-e25ec7997d79">
<p local-id=3D"c8f0c5683377">ECS Service (2 tasks running)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81a97736-aac4-4574-a209-6eeb70b2d7a7">
<p local-id=3D"b19b04bb3aea">Application Load Balancer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"91f7153a-624d-4f7a-829d-89d5b3230441">
<p local-id=3D"3a682d8d2f12">Target Group</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2011c893-1021-4d6f-8783-8880fa477059">
<p local-id=3D"d391f65aaa28">Security Groups</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"49d0d9c0c898"><strong>Request Flow</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"54119056bede">User =E2=86=92 ALB (Port 80)<br>
ALB =E2=86=92 Target Group (Port 3000)<br>
Target Group =E2=86=92 ECS Fargate Task<br>
Task =E2=86=92 Node.js Container</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0ab1da4e-9067-45aa-a0ab-4abcb8d1c99e">
<p local-id=3D"5a10c41e4851"><strong>3.2 Environment</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"ddb26a0004a5">Only one environment was created:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c1084bdb-a544-4196-bcc7-a266fd023ab1">
<li local-id=3D"fd6b6a28-beaa-4c3c-987c-0a64109b59e9">
<p local-id=3D"0e50a88f659d">Production (single deployment)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a3caa763891d">No separate dev or staging environment was con=
figured.</p>
