<hr local-id=3D"3a13a993-e9fb-46f4-889d-4818b04de8ce">
<p local-id=3D"f42523c568d4"><strong>3.4 Application Architecture &amp; Sec=
ured User Flow</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a00b795d02e7">Architecture:</p>
<p local-id=3D"dcd04a22c90a">Internet<br>
=E2=86=92 Application Load Balancer (Public)<br>
=E2=86=92 Target Group<br>
=E2=86=92 ECS Service<br>
=E2=86=92 Fargate Tasks (2 containers)<br>
=E2=86=92 Node.js App</p>
<p local-id=3D"86f295f6c362">Security Model:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"432c3250-14de-4a57-b940-6b4b117a43fe">
<li local-id=3D"d0d1fed4-ee43-4260-920f-263b5d8b50c8">
<p local-id=3D"ffb70a619710">ALB allows inbound HTTP (80) from 0.0.0.0/0</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"de1d26d7-682d-4af5-8a71-a90cc60c2af0">
<p local-id=3D"000fbd90894d">ECS Task Security Group allows inbound 3000 on=
ly from ALB Security Group</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"343c2064-37f0-471c-9a70-9e846fde024a">
<p local-id=3D"8fa146ea06b5">Containers are not directly accessible publicl=
y</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9f619ab5-2167-498a-9c0a-72a30b146869">
<h1 local-id=3D"22c0af1558e6" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentPract=
ices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<p local-id=3D"cb0f5b539755"><strong>4.1 Version Control</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"bcb53fc6-9c50-474f-b712-592c2239734e">
<li local-id=3D"19899aaa-a274-4614-af5c-a821e37cde35">
<p local-id=3D"19da658be22e">Application source stored in Git repository</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc903025-9521-48a4-822d-46e997992769">
<p local-id=3D"9abaa6fcdeb0">Dockerfile created manually</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"492de67a-6ded-4035-8733-0344528b8ec6">
<p local-id=3D"3d31f7811c12">Image tagged as latest</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"25884cfeddf2">No branching strategy was implemented.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c30b5919-0d3d-44c2-98ca-945c2f33078d">
<p local-id=3D"549d958b6915"><strong>4.2 Continuous Integration</strong></p=
>
<p local-id=3D"3921e99f2cbd">Build and push process was manual:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"20f9da0e-cf80-4c87-9374-ef6329682ebc">
<li local-id=3D"8be51c2e-99b0-4703-a028-c723a1e6282e">
<p local-id=3D"12a8b93db29a">docker build</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee1017f9-1790-422a-83cc-6e28f4a4e48d">
<p local-id=3D"a4146be644f0">docker tag</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6883d368-09f1-4723-962f-97c56092e0ed">
<p local-id=3D"0b5ba3022185">docker push to ECR</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"203592bf478e">No automated CI pipeline was used.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6ee166d6-3118-4b18-924d-4bd19ab9e250">
<p local-id=3D"b4fe838c544d"><strong>4.3 Automated Testing</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"831f285d9c7e">Basic testing performed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1b227a69-cb4f-4b40-991d-8586303551ec">
<li local-id=3D"bbf4eb87-b3d6-4a3b-9588-2b977e9ff7db">
<p local-id=3D"40c00b6cefd7">Local container test using docker run</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b94c288-40e3-4972-a388-1b847a6034c1">
<p local-id=3D"6463bf39559b">Health check validation via ALB</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b1bb8249120b">No automated test framework integrated.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a03b3a19-d64d-4be9-ae44-407453cd65f6">
<p local-id=3D"8ec54a2923ef"><strong>4.4 Code Quality</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"9814a63486a5">No external code analysis tools used.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6cd30a362fc1">Validation was done by:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"404a815d-dc80-4ce9-b299-9777a05b6ba8">
<li local-id=3D"3a7d9671-94c1-4cc2-995d-4ea2e04ff06b">
<p local-id=3D"f84c12ff1a26">Successful Docker build</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c1511fe-10d4-41f3-a058-248e27d027f6">
<p local-id=3D"d02ec7d917bc">Successful container run</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e2445fc-ef6d-4576-9379-36c677f20352">
<p local-id=3D"0138497d657a">Health check passing</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"cd01136265f1" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-5.DeploymentandRel=
easeManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"870a4973d03a"><strong>5.1 Deployment Strategy</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"2609155d6847">Deployment was performed manually via:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"18bfa58c-1f89-4125-a7e1-34f72e42dd29">
<li local-id=3D"1db1662f-a6c5-4b9b-ab8c-5b932e791dc7">
<p local-id=3D"c80b3fd0fd82">ECS Task Definition creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c06966f-b3b4-498b-8312-a276b913a3ea">
<p local-id=3D"32a86e6f8063">ECS Service creation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b461c282753d">ECS uses rolling deployment by default:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"70c9471a-6f69-4816-8309-a75b6938426d">
<li local-id=3D"87a709a0-77a7-4874-8d68-cede6eebb146">
<p local-id=3D"5dc09ec01274">New tasks start</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b093f0e1-b3e4-4f10-9e33-5e08ee7d4357">
<p local-id=3D"d45cb0dc0112">Health check verifies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5a98fbb-62bb-49c2-b733-eb52aa9329d6">
<p local-id=3D"cb2aaacff29c">Service maintains desired count</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"101de544-e08d-4fd2-8553-9919d91dcde7">
<p local-id=3D"2062427b5cfb"><strong>5.2 Configuration Management</strong><=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"82da5047d81b">Configuration done manually through:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b7a432a0-fc68-4daa-8fd1-1e79aa0e0c58">
<li local-id=3D"3110b857-af4a-4d3f-b55f-0072a359b3ba">
<p local-id=3D"e34250d3ddba">AWS Console</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19d1b1ed-6b13-4ee6-b95c-a717f99a1e7b">
<p local-id=3D"561f6d78c16a">Security Group rules</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e6c89a07-9bc2-49cf-8c5a-6fb14143d0ac">
<p local-id=3D"02148299fea6">Task Definition parameters</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"26d2e52ba971">No Infrastructure as Code used.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"f341928d-abe8-4ef7-8e55-2d4eec5866e8">
<p local-id=3D"8c04718ea5f4"><strong>5.3 Continuous Delivery</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"1de29900f318">No automated CD pipeline.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8201920ac298">Deployment steps:</p>
<p local-id=3D"c3279d9b34b4">Docker =E2=86=92 ECR =E2=86=92 ECS Service</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3b9759cf-cdda-49d4-998c-9a45c4882ecc">
<h1 local-id=3D"1e93e30930a7" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-6.MonitoringandInc=
identHandling">6. Monitoring and Incident Handling</h1>
