<p local-id=3D"06bfe6c3ef74">Target group showing 2 healthy targets</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6a179d98-c654-4773-b43c-05b2df48f553">
<p local-id=3D"efba693e5e43"><strong>6.2 Alerting</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"20396661227b">No alerting system configured.</p>
<p local-id=3D"47e2e8741162">Monitoring performed manually via AWS Console.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a2155955-3563-4b4a-8a46-c58997694ad8">
<p local-id=3D"c5fefd5b313a"><strong>6.3 Incident Handling</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"050467108eff">If a task fails:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9569be48-2365-48ea-929b-fe42afdc5f08">
<li local-id=3D"de82749b-f7ff-4095-8c4e-7549c23d8962">
<p local-id=3D"5f0ad0fb1b95">ECS automatically restarts the container</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"0dfcaedf-a761-4cc4-a741-b28a73118ad7">
<p local-id=3D"f6efd151b0d9">ALB removes unhealthy targets</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5260f0b2144d">This behavior was observed during debugging.</=
p>
<hr local-id=3D"42d8457b-a72f-43da-b56a-971803f6071a">
<h1 local-id=3D"dbd061befb7d" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp;Com=
pliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"341f7b73afc2">Security measures implemented:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1915f92f-8c98-4234-83d8-8af471c3745c">
<li local-id=3D"8d56ea5e-e6fe-47c5-9a7c-84c6ecb58194">
<p local-id=3D"d9ae0ada619f">Private ECR repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab0125cd-b7ce-43c4-bfc3-d406d626ada8">
<p local-id=3D"86da88813a8e">IAM-based authentication for ECR push</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afcee18a-0ebf-4694-b15a-5df759cd284d">
<p local-id=3D"239988519c4e">ALB as only public entry point</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9ee94a7-c00d-4291-b074-1b912122c3f3">
<p local-id=3D"302a2a99f230">ECS containers isolated in private networking<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0909aa12-d9a8-46b3-8e03-46ffcebc5145">
<p local-id=3D"dcc4d53169a0">Security group restricting port 3000 access on=
ly from ALB</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"be521c59d284" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-8.CostConsideratio=
n">8. Cost Consideration</h1>
<p local-id=3D"522441d1725d">Cost factors involved:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1ecb63bd-985d-4ad6-ab68-73466bb47dbe">
<li local-id=3D"617582bc-7195-4a0f-849a-ea215b872bb1">
<p local-id=3D"7cad8abf6296">Fargate (256 CPU / 512MB per task)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b93cb22b-5952-4f9a-b9e7-6d3f2a2aaa0f">
<p local-id=3D"998f8cac93f0">2 running tasks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4738b18-85df-45b7-87ae-e784a3b71640">
<p local-id=3D"c3aed8abf49a">Application Load Balancer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c5bac5a-eeb9-413e-9047-f5cffe804665">
<p local-id=3D"4dd016ba3cca">ECR storage</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4bee473f0307">No detailed TCO modeling was performed.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3bed31a5cce1">This setup avoids EC2 instance cost.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c1fa03ee-393e-4e05-920e-f83168833ea1">
<h1 local-id=3D"ec74ba059bab" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-9.ImplementationTi=
meline">9. Implementation Timeline</h1>
<p local-id=3D"eaa93cedf7d1">Phase 1: Docker Setup &amp; Image Build<br>
Phase 2: ECR Push<br>
Phase 3: ECS Cluster &amp; Service Deployment<br>
Phase 4: Debugging ALB &amp; Target Group</p>
<p local-id=3D"47d667e18e0f">Completed within lab session timeframe.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"2a78157b-339a-49aa-a58b-9dc92c12ec7f">
<h1 local-id=3D"6a9365420b6e" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-10.ContinuousImpro=
vement">10. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c43e8d5829f8">Improvements identified during debugging:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"df2a8b14-1a5a-4dd1-ba8e-9b80dcf5e32e">
<li local-id=3D"3ff99d16-38d1-408a-b6bf-f52fd2811452">
<p local-id=3D"363b58e9bb79">Correct target group port (3000 instead of 80)=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca7b733d-08db-4e12-9156-4973ab1fd739">
<p local-id=3D"3caa3e000f0a">Proper security group configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff381ed8-7ad8-4ad4-bc3b-376789547d13">
<p local-id=3D"b57d0be04fd6">Ensuring container port mapping matches ALB co=
nfiguration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e1b38c76-c26e-4337-9c5d-fa43de84d9ae">
<h1 local-id=3D"dc549da16f19" id=3D"T1-TechnicalDocument-11.Conclusion">11.=
 Conclusion</h1>
