<p local-id=3D"1ccafa143293">The Node.js application was successfully:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9395dc10-6285-454d-9623-4dab16f48d6b">
<li local-id=3D"aea0a2bf-6d31-4491-be0d-12946eb75b35">
<p local-id=3D"dc0ed3b28cb4">Containerized using Docker</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78a5e7df-4dd5-4f2e-b076-456c769a19d3">
<p local-id=3D"893267b844bf">Stored in Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"708e9a94-1c10-4e6d-b5b1-37d9dd2a9c28">
<p local-id=3D"7ae2c0fbd3ce">Deployed using ECS Fargate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22e6cbe9-95d9-4052-b6eb-220277df7fec">
<p local-id=3D"fad31e35735d">Load balanced using ALB</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fa88d76-3d6e-488d-bb95-a7287f8325db">
<p local-id=3D"00a6c4e7027b">Secured via proper security groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4cb075d3-f879-4e24-a2b5-da65a165ad80">
<p local-id=3D"e0f0d710d051">Configured for high availability with 2 tasks<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a18dde71d1e6">This implementation demonstrates a working con=
tainer-based deployment on AWS without managing EC2 servers.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c853c12fca42">&nbsp;</p>
    </div>
